——Revision A, 02/17/2023.
- Overhauled most of everything.
- Deprecated `Print 2`.
- New user interface (UI2).
- Progressive web application (PWA).
- Form:
  - `Back contents visibility`.
  - `Reset Cover`.
  - `Reverse`.
  - `Short spine` (0.4 in).
  - Changed no-save marker to '+'.
  - Heading for upper and lower note contents.
  - Moved `Outline` to print shop.
  - Replaced "Content" with "Contents".
  - Replaced deprecated HTML styling tags with CSS equivalents.
  - `Short back` tooltip (0.6 in).
- Help:
  - About.
  - Preview marker (β).
- Load:
  - Load cover (separately).
  - Print empty MIME types.
- Preview:
  - Center template.
  - Wrap template with <output>.
- Print:
  - Established print shop.
  - `Count`.
  - `Margin`.
  - `Opacity`.
  - `Start`.
- Save:
  - Custom file name.
  - Download cover (separately).
- Script:
  - Conditional listening of the `beforeunload` event.
  - Modularized everything where sensible.
  - Safe values.
- Template:
  - `Outline` no longer on preview.
  - Redone preset cover.
  - Variablized metrics.
- UI:
  - Capitalize only the first character of field labels.
  - Collapsible fieldsets (accordions).
  - Length limits on string fields.
- UI1:
  - Jump menu entries open outside the window.
  - Link to UI2.
- Window:
  - Replaced favicon with cover.

